<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ROUZE - Market Intelligence</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0033 0%, #2d1b4e 50%, #0f3a5a 100%);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            color: #B0A6DF;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #B0A6DF;
        }
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #B0A6DF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #3A8FC3;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 52px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3A8FC3;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 48px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: rgba(58, 143, 195, 0.9);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .pricing-section {
            padding: 80px 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .pricing-card {
            background: rgba(82, 66, 92, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176, 166, 223, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(45px);
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .pricing-card:hover {
            background: rgba(82, 66, 92, 0.4);
            border-color: rgba(58, 143, 195, 0.5);
        }
        .price {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #3A8FC3;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .timeline {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
            nav ul { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
            .hero { padding: 40px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">ROUZE</div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/methodology">Methodology</a></li>
            <li><a href="/pricing">Pricing</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Transform Raw Signals Into Strategic Advantage</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Market intelligence in 24-48 hours. Not 3-6 months. Not surveys. Real customer conversations.</p>
        <a href="/vertical-selector" class="cta-button">Start Free Analysis</a>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-section">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 36px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">Pricing</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 40px;">Three tiers. One mission: Give you market truth.</p>
        
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Quick Intelligence</h3>
                <div class="price">$300-800</div>
                <div class="timeline">24-48 hours</div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">Fast market validation. Perfect for launch decisions.</p>
                <a href="/vertical-selector" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 32px;">Choose</a>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Strategic Intelligence</h3>
                <div class="price">$800-2,000</div>
                <div class="timeline">5-7 days</div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">Deep analysis. Competitive positioning. Market strategy.</p>
                <a href="/vertical-selector" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 32px;">Choose</a>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Predictive Intelligence</h3>
                <div class="price">$2,000-5,000</div>
                <div class="timeline">10-14 days</div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">Forecasting. Scenario planning. Risk assessment.</p>
                <a href="/vertical-selector" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 32px;">Choose</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
